## Whatâ€™s Next?
HackViolet hackathon provides a safe and welcoming enviornment for people of any identity to participate, learn, code, and experience a hackathon. We have a solid participation rate from our local Virginia Tech community, but also with various Virginian universities and other East Coast universities as well. We strive to empower our participants to become agents of change and support minorities in the field of computing and technology. From HackViolet 2024, we saw an increase in attendees and workshop participation, and we aim to keep this growth continued for many years. The tentative dates for our future hackathon are Feb. 1st to 2nd, 2025.

